descriptionHtml:
Edhildils Bug Armor
Author: Edhildil
04,09,2018
ver1

Adds a Chest in Whiterun that has DMRA Bug Armor. Please enjoy the humor.

This could be good for a follower or an enemy in your mod. If you want to use/convert please just credit me (Edhildil).

You'll need CBBE textures.
You'll need Dawnguard.

If you want Bodyslide, UNP, 7base, HDT physics, etc, I'm not going to do it, but if you can, you can. Just credit me.
If you can't, somebody probably will.

Tools used:
=======
Blender 2.49b
Gimp 2
Nifscope
